Check DM State For Datasets

Source: R/DM_Server.R
DM_hasds.Rd

Walks through the DM state object to see if there are any datasets available

Usage

DM_hasds(state)

Arguments

state

DM state from DM_fetch_state()

Value

Logical TRUE if there is a dataset or FALSE otherwise.

Examples

sess_res = DM_test_mksession()
